        "content": "# PII / guardrails\n\nDetectors run on every prompt **and** every output. Hits show up here.\n\nCategories: credit cards, SSNs, API keys (sk-ant-, sk-, ghp-), email, phone, addresses. The SailPoint transcript flagged this as a critical use case — they explicitly want alerts when an API key appears in chat traffic.",
